/-! ## Parsing infrastructure (consumed by `csBlockSigmaInfo` and
    `csBlockBasis`).

The data is shipped as two String literals: `sigmaInfoStr` (278
records of `σ_size-σ_id-outer_size-dim-σ_hex`) and `sigmaBasisStr` (278
